<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>١٥٩. تعملون<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>...<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
